### The rules ###

1. The talks will be presented on a stage in [Meskalina café bar](Venue.html). Expect relaxed and informal gathering.
2. Each talk will be exactly 321 seconds.
3. We are not going to curate the content of the talks. It is completely up to the speakers if they want to be entertaining or formal. We do not mind commercial talks, but we may want to limit their number.
4. Wearing shorts is not obligatory.

